eted triangular\nlattice. The classical character of the AHM for small $s$ is also detected on\nthe ground state energy and correlation functions. On the other hand the\nclassical magnetization discontinuity in a field eventually disappears for\nsmall $s$, after a weak reentrant behavior.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Oct 2014 19:16:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
