risations. This suggests that further fundamental insight is needed\ninto the problem of statistical consistency of phylogenetic inference methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Oct 2014 00:47:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2015 06:06:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 23 Sep 2015 03:58:37 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 17 Mar 2016 00:45:18 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 9 Jun 2016 03:35:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-10"}
