an occur very early in the star formation\nprocess, coeval with or just after the formation of a first hydrostatic core or\nprotostar.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Oct 2014 14:25:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
